      "id": "mem-feedback_openpyxl_charts----",
      "content": "name: openpyxl chart gotchas\ndescription: Hard-won lessons from debugging openpyxl chart generation for the Rollup Framework Excel\ntype: feedback\n---\n\nopenpyxl 3.1.5 chart generation has several non-obvious pitfalls:\n\n1. **BubbleChart corrupts drawing XML on existing worksheets** — works on fresh workbooks but produces \"Removed Part: drawing1.xml\" error when added to sheets that previously had charts. Use ScatterChart instead.\n\n2. **Scatter series `dLbls.showLegendKey` must be explicitly False**",
      "summary": "---",
